<! [CDATA[
Graphite Enterprise Trust Logo
ICG Enterprise Trust plc is an investment company. It is listed on the London Stock Exchange and is a constituent of the FTSE 250 Index of the largest listed companies. In particular it is one of the largest investment trusts on the stock exchange with a market capitalisation of £579 million as at 13 March 2020. Its objective is to provide shareholders with long-term capital growth through investment in unquoted companies, though private equity funds and also directly.
